92
00:06:19,595 --> 00:06:21,295
Misteri apa?

93
00:06:21,295 --> 00:06:23,795
Kyoko, apa kau tahu sesuatu?

94
00:06:23,795 --> 00:06:26,095
Aku belum bisa memberitahumu.

95
00:06:26,095 --> 00:06:29,195
Aku sedang menunggu hingga polisi tiba.

96
00:06:29,195 --> 00:06:32,195
Karena, aku mungkin salah.

97
00:06:35,495 --> 00:06:37,295
Hei, Ran.

98
00:06:37,295 --> 00:06:39,095
Ingin pergi ke kamar kecil bersama?

99
00:06:39,095 --> 00:06:40,395
Baik.

