165
00:10:11,095 --> 00:10:14,295
Kalian berdua bawa paman itu ke atas!

166
00:10:15,395 --> 00:10:16,495
Tapi, Heiji...

167
00:10:16,495 --> 00:10:17,995
Jangan cemas!

168
00:10:17,995 --> 00:10:20,895
