00:12:20,221 --> 00:12:22,821
Hei, pria besar!

191
00:12:22,821 --> 00:12:24,921
Apa kau pemimpin mereka?

192
00:12:31,121 --> 00:12:33,721
Aku sudah membunuhnya!

193
00:12:33,721 --> 00:12:36,321
